1. Purpose

This Thorn implements the weak rates necessary to compute emissions and
opacities assuming that the neutrinos absorbed, scattered and emitted are in
thermal and chemical equilibrium with the matter. The energy and number
distributions are also assumed to follow a Fermi ditribution at equilibrium.
